{"tid":1617611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港會唔會重演烏克蘭嘅悲劇？","createTime":"2019-10-04T00:29:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T05:39:37.000Z","uid":127479,"like":484,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":92,"replies":[{"pid":"86e9453fb1ecda03268de88d1eb27144fdb303f6","tid":1617611,"uid":127479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T00:29:43.000Z","msg":"《凜冬烈火》只是烏克蘭悲劇的上集。當烏克蘭人以為打贏阿努科維奇就可以解放全國的時候，緊隨其後的卻是克里米亞被「吞併」&mdash;&mdash;吞併這個字眼有點兒誤導，事實上俄羅斯沒有使用大軍。<span style=\"color: orange;\">普京最厲害的地方，是以民主之道還治民主之身，收復克里米亞，是靠發動一場「自決公投」。</span><br />\n<br />\n在親俄的省議員帶領下，以及在親歐的烏克蘭人韃靼人的杯葛下，公投以97%高票通過獨立。儘管基輔和聯合國多數都不承認公投結果，仍難阻克里米亞政府加入俄羅斯聯邦。普京完成了分裂烏克蘭的第一步。<br />\n<br />\n第二步，輪到蟄伏在烏東兩省的親俄分子發動「自決公投」，克里米亞可以，為甚麼頓涅茨克不可以？當時就有人說希特勒也是靠公投來吞併奧地利。不過普京很聰明，今次他沒有「吞併」這兩個新立的共和國，而是讓它們繼續留在烏克蘭「境內」，破壞基輔的總統選舉和發動內戰。五年間足足13,000人喪生。<br />\n<br />\n普京的宏願是收復烏克蘭，而烏克蘭要護國就不得不反俄，所以在今年的大選，齊齊拒絕了親俄的波羅申科，捧起了政治素人、喜劇演員澤連斯基。<br />\n<br />\n你又以為民主又贏一仗嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">澤連斯基背後其實有財閥支持，控制了一個政治明星，你就可以控制一個國家&mdash;&mdash;如果他也是普京的傀儡怎麼辦？</span><br />\n<br />\n他一上台，就急於推動烏俄協議，與普京通了兩次電話，合謀達成了破天荒的俘虜交換。烏克蘭其中一個釋放的人質，還要係那位有份用山毛櫸導彈擊落MH17的軍官，嚇到荷蘭的調查團立即要求押後換囚，趕赴基輔，把握盤問的最後機會。<br />\n<br />\n輿論當然會包裝成「邁向烏東和平又近一步」，這也是澤連斯基的政綱之一，所以他更進一步，在10月1日開任內第二次記者會，宣布啟動Steinmeier Formula。<br />\n<br />\nSteinmeier係德國的前外長，由於俄烏在白俄羅斯簽過兩次明斯克和議都沒法停止戰火，Steinmeier就中膽提出一個新方案：烏克蘭容許兩省舉行公投成為自治區，以換取兩省交出烏俄邊境的控制權。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">這不是很可笑嗎？當初基輔開戰就是為了否定普京發動的自決公投，轉個頭卻肯定了它，還對得住死去的兄弟嗎？</span><br />\n<br />\n普京聽到澤連斯基終於肯首，自然心花怒放，因為擺平了這個問題，意味歐盟對俄的經濟制裁亦可以告終。這個Formula，馬克龍與默克爾都有份遊說&mdash;&mdash;因為他們都想跟俄羅斯做回生意。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">烏克蘭人怎麼想？大部分人都六神無主，只有敏銳的人知道是甚麼一回事，去到政總抗議：不要投降！不要投降！簽協議即是投降！</span><br />\n<br />\n諷刺的是，波羅申科也說，不應該簽，放任自決即係投降。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">民主的初哥們，你們玩得起這種新型民主嗎？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">我預視到，香港極有可能重演烏克蘭的悲劇。<br />\n<br />\n2047自決公投？<br />\n<br />\n到那時，香港人已被洗血得七七八八，中共在普京的教導下，當然支持發動自決公投。在反對派杯葛的情況下，大灣區香港片區以97%高票通過實施一國一制。</span><br />\n<br />\n難道老來的你又要再上街，再做文宣，再求國際聲援嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">克里米亞那一萬個烏克蘭居民，尚且可遷徙至基輔，我們呢？<br />\n<br />\n我們的政治水平可否再提高一點，以免被吞併的悲劇重演？<br />\n<br />\n歷史就在眼前，你卻任由自己一無所知，怎可以這樣？</span><br />\n<br />\n作者<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UCiqGwC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUCiqGwC.jpg&h=33b0402c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1aa5eac4532da0b9a6a547165ae689cd4599a6ef","tid":1617611,"uid":127479,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T00:37:35.000Z","msg":"「軍事」「香港」「漫畫多圖」《最於解決方案》<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1615112\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1615112</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oesKW8Q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoesKW8Q.png&h=10a62f58&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d8f2c2ea60763a7bb2283fceccdd992dc8ced826","tid":1617611,"uid":127479,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T00:38:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/teuhxHi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FteuhxHi.png&h=d1b2b7af&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"79482cfb4da0483bbf19321fc79cbef0a8e82e4c","tid":1617611,"uid":127479,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T00:38:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2z3x52r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2z3x52r.png&h=a50e46fa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6a7aaef6aae96ced53781537b30f1a7ddc80c184","tid":1617611,"uid":127479,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T00:38:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qjYBOfR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqjYBOfR.png&h=13d2c286&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7908a98e38e5a2477868df435fbf1a3609886bf4","tid":1617611,"uid":11040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T00:38:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a10d4d7c1f78e639f0af1a7aaec274ffb631d301","tid":1617611,"uid":260694,"like":47,"dislike":2,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T00:39:45.000Z","msg":"似十足，開完槍之後蒙面法<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee52a6c0e24c24e7602dfa90c8615626cf56c07a","tid":1617611,"uid":143260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T00:40:54.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e755058155cf0f37b71c84d997cdd044f1df19e7","tid":1617611,"uid":127479,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T00:47:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NxgS55s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNxgS55s.jpg&h=4a5edd70&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f05de6b902212eca88bf90a794dc93ebd7fc6808","tid":1617611,"uid":127479,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T00:48:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UYEhxLL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUYEhxLL.jpg&h=99d479f1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"33a8612f14eb1f1536cc0ef7e9d3a491c577d2d5","tid":1617611,"uid":65738,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T00:53:22.000Z","msg":"烏克蘭嘅悲劇係今時今日對支那人好感度仍然極高，佢地究竟覺醒左D咩"},{"pid":"5641dd7fae613ef7d961c669bdef169505d424bb","tid":1617611,"uid":278786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T00:54:01.000Z","msg":"唔好畀淋病spin走！！！錯重點！！！<br />\n萬一正苦真係用緊急法推蒙面法，焦點應放在緊急法！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1617518/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1617518/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"fc4014bd344a5e83e84e4f8cd5ccc646143f9ebb","tid":1617611,"uid":273852,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T01:00:36.000Z","msg":"1999"},{"pid":"35afe7eab5eeef3e59ee37493c76d02e9209a987","tid":1617611,"uid":41205,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T01:08:51.000Z","msg":"上水 屯門 天水圍公投？"},{"pid":"9fc87a79299b3aa5c5eb655d05967cd3c0cb5f87","tid":1617611,"uid":34927,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"fc4014bd344a5e83e84e4f8cd5ccc646143f9ebb","tid":1617611,"uid":273852,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T01:00:36.000Z","msg":"1999"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T01:10:32.000Z","msg":"係要細心睇先明<br />\n可能因為個背景我地唔熟，但絕對有益"},{"pid":"b7d296571949731fae8e4d2b5a13079b0ebed28c","tid":1617611,"uid":25108,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T01:11:21.000Z","msg":"問題係佢口口聲聲話親歐<br />\n暗地就俄羅斯既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b38444937345d55b5a2d6b6f448464706f01b6c","tid":1617611,"uid":25108,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"b7d296571949731fae8e4d2b5a13079b0ebed28c","tid":1617611,"uid":25108,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T01:11:21.000Z","msg":"問題係佢口口聲聲話親歐<br />\n暗地就俄羅斯既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T01:12:19.000Z","msg":"情況有啲似咩素人落區<br />\n投完原來共產黨"},{"pid":"c7631aafd46dce868bcd0540d87c61293517b705","tid":1617611,"uid":2404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T01:14:15.000Z","msg":"香港人冇時間喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96553baa6504775ad653685441f61e813ee22e17","tid":1617611,"uid":61882,"like":90,"dislike":0,"score":90,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T01:15:06.000Z","msg":"現實係你地同共產黨打緊交道<br />\n你地點會用對抗民主政府既思維黎搞抗爭<br />\n對極權政府黎講權力就係佢既生命<br />\n係半點都唔會退讓<br />\n就算比你搵到佢個春袋又點姐<br />\n唔通佢會話哎呀你搵到我個春袋啦我投降啦<br />\n然後就自爆啦咩<br />\n唔會架嘛<br />\n就算比你揸住佢個春袋佢都只會親手打爆自己個春袋然後再打爆你<br />\n<br />\n如果你話共產黨係講利益既佢有好多錢係香港佢唔敢玩盡既<br />\n你講得岩<br />\n共產黨係講利益既<br />\n權力就係佢既利益<br />\n利益就黎自佢既權力<br />\n你幾時見過黑社會收陀地要幫埋人地做生意?<br />\n佢坐係呢個位就應份食你地既<br />\n你交唔足數就你自己過主<br />\n佢寧願匿係個山窿入面做大王都唔會係個城市入面做平民<br />\n所以點解窮到北韓咁肥仔金都會無動於衷<br />\n呢D就係共產黨思維<br />\n同呢種極權政府同佢玩到咁大仲叫&quot;爭取&quot;&quot;訴求&quot;<br />\n你地呢D咪叫大種乞衣囉<br />\n<br />\n你地接受好唔接受好<br />\n你地而家搞緊既就係香港獨立革命<br />\n你地想好唔想好<br />\n你地遲早要面對一場香港獨立戰爭<br />\n拋棄左膠黃絲既苟且<br />\n拋棄冷氣軍事D八奇思維<br />\n我地往後既行動必須向呢個方向做準備<br />\n你地背負既未來比你可以想像既嚴重得多<br />\n往後呢幾日我雖唔敢話係最後一戰<br />\n你地崖唔過既等緊你地既就係新疆北韓<br />\n崖過左既就係香港既全面內戰<br />\n<br />\n光復香港時代革命呢D口號已經太幼稚<br />\n以後要嗌既將會係打倒軍政府"},{"pid":"1ae88450f72dff1e338aaefe7ea4b8288cd984fa","tid":1617611,"uid":57081,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T01:16:39.000Z","msg":"2047公投 我勤大家早日移民吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecada633f745139563cb2c00eb99bdbf451d1938","tid":1617611,"uid":57081,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1ae88450f72dff1e338aaefe7ea4b8288cd984fa","tid":1617611,"uid":57081,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T01:16:39.000Z","msg":"2047公投 我勤大家早日移民吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T01:17:30.000Z","msg":"勸"},{"pid":"0cd284985afeb0e7f9c5327f4a11480c058c0b8f","tid":1617611,"uid":145254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T01:18:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0b5117e0f910e4338adba3816df136b7805b6e3","tid":1617611,"uid":165113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T01:20:14.000Z","msg":"其實更加會似Hungary咁比人鎮壓多啲"},{"pid":"d266138cbda8c3942e1d52394ec7ae6a340ccf1c","tid":1617611,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96553baa6504775ad653685441f61e813ee22e17","tid":1617611,"uid":61882,"like":90,"dislike":0,"score":90,"citedBy":6,"replyT