,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T05:32:51.000Z","msg":"習近平老羞成怒<br />\n國慶日血流成河<br />\n佢唔會CARE<br />\n佢會覺得自己勁過鄧小平<br />\n佢會覺得自己媲美毛澤東<br />\n歷史選擇了香港<br />\n大家與有榮焉"},{"pid":"f2a785dd59d2019b9d5c034997d6bebb0150f17f","tid":1617611,"uid":143399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T05:36:13.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fd2f7e3656b9d2a52b42ca4e5f6939d55b2e8e8","tid":1617611,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T05:37:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed4a64178ded0a5213f709efdca8c71fb32030a9","tid":1617611,"uid":149161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T05:38:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e6982cfb88993fd4dc5e0902b40b560cb5dd73e","tid":1617611,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T05:39:14.000Z","msg":"老實講 唔會"},{"pid":"d53ab6ba15a272f9f7ac0559c8e6ccd4a931f7d7","tid":1617611,"uid":172102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T05:40:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4ba5e4370bd7efafc165fe510942823142350d71","tid":1617611,"uid":13428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T05:41:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09b498a0e8f0a17dd6843d887d2945e98b652bf0","tid":1617611,"uid":72863,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T05:42:39.000Z","msg":"大家都怕，但更怕將來睇唔到光"},{"pid":"3b84671fc117d90e97c8fd4eb5ac9d6b75873d92","tid":1617611,"uid":328418,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T05:43:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5478a7607f849cc75183126a9314700c42cd2194","tid":1617611,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T05:43:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"062cace5b1290f8406d3e93356543ab0718af4c3","tid":1617611,"uid":127479,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T05:47:01.000Z","msg":"Facebook post 精選留言：<br />\n香港過去的繁榮穩定、社會安全的確冇誘因使人關注學習政情，個個假手於代理人，任人擺佈至今，過往呢度最大的優勢變成今日最大的劣勢<br />\n最大鑊的係，唔識咪認、踏實啲去學，但佢地又唔會 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n作者，看了這二百多個的留言沮喪了嗎？還有更多沒有留意的人，這就是所謂百姓，也就是民意。<br />\n<br />\n世界的現實就是這樣，大部分的人只求安逸，思維模式依賴。要認清事實，才能做出正確決定，2047眨眼就到，香港不能只在自己區域被動，必須出擊。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n所以成日都話，就算有真普選，真正既民主之戰係之後既選舉。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n雖然俄羅斯現在已不是共產主義意識，但前蘇聯的種族文化滅絕卻是世界上最成功的，超過希特拉。前蘇聯的加盟共和國、（外） 蒙古等，特別是中亞的幾個伊斯蘭國家，以前都是有自己的語言、文字，而共產70年後，文字書寫變成了俄文，雖然口語還可以保存 原來的，如外蒙古的蒙文與內蒙古的蒙文，中亞現在的文字與伊朗的文字... 已完全無法溝通，雖然曾是同一民族。哼，看看北面，再想想HK未來，會怎樣.... 還用問麼，一個族群，只要把你的身份意識、文字語言給 抹滅掉，就死亡了"},{"pid":"63a003ae59553dc0cf73bfd1d3cc0b6dad45a5d4","tid":1617611,"uid":278038,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T05:47:53.000Z","msg":"我覺得不能將克里米亞同香港類比。<br />\n<br />\n克里米亞係蘇聯時代俄羅斯向烏克蘭贈送示好，人口一直俄羅斯人為主俄語為主，人根本真係俄羅斯人黎。"},{"pid":"0303b5f6584b45d83e0c8c962f9b830ededa237c","tid":1617611,"uid":315833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T05:50:51.000Z","msg":"烏克蘭背後就係歐洲，係北約<br />\n<br />\n香港係東亞，無武力支援唔夠打的"},{"pid":"2e7c9591d415f9155c98e162f8260789ff47fdb6","tid":1617611,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T05:52:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5e92cb6cd19743bb040d327bc3501912fa2baa9","tid":1617611,"uid":308618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"96553baa6504775ad653685441f61e813