ot;&quot;訴求&quot;<br />\n你地呢D咪叫大種乞衣囉<br />\n<br />\n你地接受好唔接受好<br />\n你地而家搞緊既就係香港獨立革命<br />\n你地想好唔想好<br />\n你地遲早要面對一場香港獨立戰爭<br />\n拋棄左膠黃絲既苟且<br />\n拋棄冷氣軍事D八奇思維<br />\n我地往後既行動必須向呢個方向做準備<br />\n你地背負既未來比你可以想像既嚴重得多<br />\n往後呢幾日我雖唔敢話係最後一戰<br />\n你地崖唔過既等緊你地既就係新疆北韓<br />\n崖過左既就係香港既全面內戰<br />\n<br />\n光復香港時代革命呢D口號已經太幼稚<br />\n以後要嗌既將會係打倒軍政府"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:19:48.000Z","msg":"同意從來真普選都係偽名題<br />\n只係爭取自治嘅其中一個手段而已"},{"pid":"29ef4f083beff1e7a7399d84c48a5a512b518dda","tid":1617611,"uid":61106,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:23:39.000Z","msg":"唔會，香港人邊敢打，射爆眼仲係叫口號"},{"pid":"cf5e97f7965a64e452f6e1ff56fa81f91ee6f2f0","tid":1617611,"uid":289035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:24:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NChOGhW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNChOGhW.jpg&h=700bd9a9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"59474dd9a0593abf489917aeaa5974b45e624747","tid":1617611,"uid":243847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:25:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"91878d520ff7c374d29c47de180f56b4a58e04be","tid":1617611,"uid":304828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:28:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ce1295227909da0d8bdd725de3b55d99277377aa","tid":1617611,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:31:50.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"009d076124db3a40df7731547e9735eb51874523","tid":1617611,"uid":240608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:34:32.000Z","msg":"烏克蘭唔係悲劇<br />\n係浴火重生"},{"pid":"a19cb62919648b3d2ce3a3ec6405dde745dd5fcf","tid":1617611,"uid":46480,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bae0399fa8aa13897910101f2f555881290ebc88","tid":161